Maintainer: Shiying Xiao <shiying.xiao@outlook.com>
Description: Provides tools for the analysis of untargeted mass spectrometry
    (MS)-based proteomics data from data-independent acquisition (DIA) and
    data-dependent acquisition (DDA) experiments. It includes tools for
    data preprocessing, transformation, filtering, normalization, differential
    abundance analysis, and visualization. It aims to support reproducible and
    statistically rigorous analysis of proteomics datasets.
